            <title>[SOLR-5567] ZkController getHostAddress duplicates url prefix</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5567</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ZkController getHostAddress method will return a URL with duplicated url prefix if given an input string already including a url prefix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;e.g. given the input &quot;http://127.0.0.1&quot;, it will return &quot;http://&lt;a href=&quot;http://127.0.0.1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://127.0.0.1&lt;/a&gt;&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
